Package: jYS
Type: Package
Title: jYS Extended Functions
Version: 1.1.4
Author: Yuri Smolyakov
Maintainer: Yuri Smolyakov <smolyakov@rambler.ru>
Description: Extensions of the functionality of popular data analysis methods:
  correlation clustering, ROC classification, missing values estimation and
  imputation, univariate and multivariate outliers identification and removal,
  Uncertain Interval (UI) threshold estimation, a priori power analysis, MLP
  neural network classifier, logistic regression with feature selection, Random
  Forest classifier, survival analysis (Kaplan-Meier and Cox regression),
  Principal Component Analysis (PCA), and Single Nucleotide Polymorphism (SNP)
  association and Hardy-Weinberg equilibrium analysis.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
